| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4633 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0af5bed5-ff3a-58c8-964b-57eb2ef1777b"
